cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper is about multilingual document classification using hierarchical attention networks. The most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with natural language processing and document classification. The second most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Learning) as the paper proposes a new model for learning document structures. The third likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper deals with document classification. The fourth likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper proposes a new model for document classification. The fifth likely sub-category is cs.DL (Deep Learning) as the paper uses deep learning techniques for document classification.
